{"tid":933494,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"比悲傷更悲傷的故事","createTime":"2018-12-08T14:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T15:56:42.000Z","uid":171898,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b90d8c0607eeecafb9d065f90c9de3ad3a510073","tid":933494,"uid":171898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"感覺到悲傷係好心痛，但更加悲哀嘅係，連悲傷都感覺唔到。<br />\n<br />\n故事係好哀傷、可惜，全場都喺度喊，但唔知點解，我真係一滴眼淚都無。唔知由幾時開始，連分手都喊唔出，個人變到好麻木。<br />\n<br />\n呢套戲我睇完除咗覺好婉惜之外，我都思考緊一樣嘢，如果講出真相會令對方受傷，到底應唔應該講？定寧願坦白，一齊去面對？"},{"pid":"c7d5d2cce22ed69b369942f953c4021284d22ab5","tid":933494,"uid":149435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"如果坦白了，一齊面對<br />\n也許最後也不會那麼悲傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad753bb6fd08133475a4c2ad94daa04fe875db1c","tid":933494,"uid":140384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"睇完你打嘅野 我一定唔會帶條女睇 費時嘈交"},{"pid":"9d6f132096f0163486165e50ba0b9b21b2d63d17","tid":933494,"uid":83531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"坦白"},{"pid":"9ca7d83e74bd73b30f9c6b1df7ec4c5eb1b8f8f4","tid":933494,"uid":171898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad753bb6fd08133475a4c2ad94daa04fe875db1c","tid":933494,"uid":140384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"睇完你打嘅野 我一定唔會帶條女睇 費時嘈交"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"我起戲院出嚟，見到幾pair情侶，女嘅問男嘅，如果我有絕症你會點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419ac61ecac48d384595c3b927ce1ee5db8e0380","tid":933494,"uid":204742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"冇嘢瞞到一世 好好面對唔好逃避啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}